Non-OSS dependencies
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Does the feature depend on any code or APIs outside the Chromium open &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;source repository and its open-source dependencies to function? &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Yes: this feature depends on a language model, which is bridged to the &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;open-source parts of the implementation via the interfaces in &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;//services/on_device_model. &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
