&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://web3dsurvey.com/"&gt;https://web3dsurvey.com/&lt;/a&gt;) then this should be seen as very much an 
