&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; that 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; is more likely to be focused on high-end devices (samples are taken 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; from 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; developer-focused sites like the three.js website, WebGPU fundamentals 
