&gt; *WebKit*: No signal;  Will file a standard-position issue.
&gt;
&gt; *Web developers*: Strongly positive (
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/2528"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/2528&lt;/a&gt;) The CSSWG issue has 90+ 
&gt; votes.
