&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Explainer
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WICG/translation-api/blob/main/README.md"&gt;https://github.com/WICG/translation-api/blob/main/README.md&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Specification
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://webmachinelearning.github.io/translation-api/#language-detector-api"&gt;https://webmachinelearning.github.io/translation-api/#language-detector-api&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Note that although the translator API and language detector APIs both
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; live in a single specification, they can be implemented independently, and
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; this Intent is only for the language detector API.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; A JavaScript API for detecting the language of text, with confidence
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; levels.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Blink component
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Blink&gt;AI&gt;Language Detection
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EAI%3ELanguage%20Detection%22"&gt;https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EAI%3ELanguage%20Detection%22&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; TAG review
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/948"&gt;https://github.com/w3ctag/design-reviews/issues/948&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; TAG review status
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Issues addressed
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; The TAG had a number of questions and suggestions, particularly around
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; API shape, all of which were addressed and incorporated into the design.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Origin Trial Name
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
