&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;  Note: The provided links are WPT for the accent-color property, 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; including scenarios where the value is set to &quot;auto.&quot; This feature 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; relies on the platform's accent color and necessitates a WebDriver 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; extension to simulate the accent-color property accurately. To ensure 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; consistent testing with WPT, we would need to look into WebDriver API 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; to support this functionality properly.
